!! <<f-i eye>> [[Google analytics plugin|G-Analytics plugin]] (sycom-{{$:/plugins/sycom/g-analytics!!version}})
the <$link to="$:/plugins/sycom/g-analytics"> <<f-i download>> Google analytics plugin</$link> is a fork of the official one you will find in the TiddlyWiki plugin library. It enables internal individual tiddlers tracking and is //Do Not Track// compliant.

!! <<f-i feather>> [[Feather icons plugin]] ({{$:/plugins/sycom/feather-icons!!version}})
the <$link to="$:/plugins/sycom/feather-icons"><<f-i download>> Feather icons plugin</$link> offers an icon library alternative to the Font Awesome one. It's pretty lightweight and elegant.

!! <<f-i rss>> [[Atom feed plugin]] ({{$:/plugins/sycom/atom-feed!!version}})
the <$link to="$:/plugins/sycom/atom-feed"><<f-i download>> Atom feed plugin</$link> will create an <a rel="alternate" href="atom.xml" target="_blank">atom.xml</a> file alongside your wiki. Helpful for people who whish follow your work.
